<body>
	<div>

		<div class="nav">
			<div class="logo-btn">
				<button type="button" onClick="parent.location='search_listing'"><img src="/images/logo.png" id="logo"></button>
			</div>
			<div class="right-align">
				<div class="menu-btn">
					<button id="menu-button" type="button" onClick="parent.location='menu'"><img src="/images/menu.png"></button>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>

		<div class="section2">
			<div class ="help-heading">
				<div class="help-title">
					FAQ
				</div>

			</div>
			<div class = "FAQ-component">
				<div class="FAQ-q">
					<p>
						What is Bookdrop?
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="FAQ-a">
					<p>
						BookDrop is an app that connects students with each other to buy and sell textbooks. The purpose of this is to provide students with a cheap alternative to buying new textbooks.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class = "FAQ-component">
				<div class="FAQ-q">
					<p>
						How do I sell textbook(s)?
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="FAQ-a">
					<p>
						You can sell textbook by creating an account and creating a listing by adding to you personal inventory. Once you add the book to your personal listing it will automatically display in the search results. Now, other users can find it!
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class = "FAQ-component">
				<div class="FAQ-q">
					<p>
						Do I need an account to sell textbook(s)?
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="FAQ-a">
					<p>
						Yes, you will need an account to create a listing.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class = "FAQ-component">
				<div class="FAQ-q">
					<p>
						Do I need an account to buy the textbook(s)?
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="FAQ-a">
					<p>
						No, you do not need an account to buy a textbook. You can directly search for the textbook without logging in/registering.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class = "FAQ-component">
				<div class="FAQ-q">
					<p>
						Why is a university email required? Can’t I just use a personal email?
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="FAQ-a">
					<p>
						For the safety of the user, we are restricting it to just students.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class = "FAQ-component">
				<div class="FAQ-q">
					<p>
						How do I contact the seller?
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="FAQ-a">
					<p>
						Great question! If you click on the book listing that you are interested in it will show a description of it. One such information is the seller’s contact information.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class = "FAQ-component">
				<div class="FAQ-q">
					<p>
						Help! I can’t save the book listing.
					</p>
				</div>
				<div class="FAQ-a">
					<p>
						Make sure that you filled out all the information. All information except the image is required to submit.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>

	</div>
